                  <origin>Completed by <persName role="scr" key="person_f2415" xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Muḥammad bin Muḥammad Jamāl</persName> in <origPlace ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7001592" key="place_7001592">Surat</origPlace> <origDate calendar="#Hijri_qamari" when="1801-02-12">28 Ramaz̤ān 1215 AH (12 Feb. 1801 CE)</origDate>.
